column5: When navigating bottleneck areas stay under control with some power and keep straight.  Or turn right for rocks.
I kept thinking, give it some power  give it some power
Almost as fun as watching boats go "down the hill" after coming out of the Marine Rail heading for Port Severn.

Bad idea to go out with the water so rough and just recently getting the boat having little experience with this boat. Then you have so many passengers on board. Maybe going faster would have prevented the boat from swaying around so much. Very tragic
